Dumb Terminal miNfo - Mediainfo Nfo Creator
Scripts to Fetch|Grab Info from IMDb

MI-NFOCreate - Uses IMDb-Dump and IMDb-ThumbGrab with MediaInfo http://mediainfo.sourceforge.net/ to Create a Custom NFO txt File for Media Files.
IMDb-Dump - Dump IMDb Movies Info to Shell or a txt File.
IMDb-ThumbGrab - Grab The Thumbnails of IMDb Movies (If Provided)
